        Initializes an instance of the RadioInfo class using the specified LTE signal parameters.
        Parameters:
        radioTimeStamp - The timestamp at which the radio information is evaluated.
        lteSignalStrength - The radio signal strength, expressed in Dbm.
        lteRsrp - The LTE Reference Signal Received Power (RSRP) value.
        lteRsrq - The LTE Reference Signal Received Quality (RSRQ) value.
        lteRssnr - The LTE Signal to Noise Ratio (SNR) value.
        lteCqi - The LTE Channel to Noise Ratio (CQI) value.
